snippet.title: Fall Guys - Release Date Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Pre-Purchase on Steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1097150/Fall_Guys_Ultimate_Knockout/

We're super hyped to announce that Fall Guys is releasing on Steam and PS4...

4th August 2020 👌

Pre-Purchase on Steam now for an exclusive outfit!
